VARIABLES

<title>{{ page.title }} - {{ site.title }}</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ '/assets/css/main.css' | relative_url }}">


Create a _data file and name it navbar.yml then add the links.
- name: Home
link: /
- name: About
link: /about
- name: Contact
link: /contact

Use this in the html to call the file:

{% for item in site.data.navbar %}
<a class="nav-item nav-link" href="{{item.link}}">{{ item.name }}</a>
{% endfor %}


IF CAROUSEL = TRUE, THEN USE THIS SCRIPT. Be sure to list carousel:true in front matter like this:
---
title: Home
carousel: true
---
<!-- Use carousel script if page has a carousel -->
{% if carousel %}
{% include carousel-script.html %}
{% endif %}